{"tid":746377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天地會咩？】網傳碧桂園員工集體飲雞血谷銷售","createTime":"2018-07-17T13:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T13:46:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e53d5dc99664ee64e3bdc65212be3881de8f61d8","tid":746377,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180716/large/1531749179_2b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180716%2Flarge%2F1531749179_2b4e.jpg&h=9210a3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳碧桂園放雞血給員工喝。(網絡圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180716/large/1531749197_54db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180716%2Flarge%2F1531749197_54db.jpg&h=46cb513f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似碧桂園員工將雞血一飲而盡。(網絡圖片)<br />\n<br />\n碧桂園（2007）傳出暫緩投地、叫停三四五線城市「全覆蓋」戰略等等，壞消息不斷。公司否認全面叫停，但承認退出部分合作非操盤項目。中國房地政策趨緊，員工都要盡力幫公司套現。<br />\n<br />\n今日在微博就傳出相片，指碧桂園福建省漳州市御江府開誓師大會，員工集體喝雞血，以振奮士氣。網友就留言「傳播禽流感」、「病態的行業、病態的單位」、「不是雞血，房地產喝的是人血！」惟公司未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n在中國，「打雞血」為在文化大革命年代曾是瘋狂蔓延的一種「保健療法」，網路上被衍生的意思為瘋狂的行為，亦被用來形容一個人特別興奮。<br />\n<br />\n碧桂園今日收報12.74元，跌2.1%。"},{"pid":"54d1a66cfa8d5b3c395702f6f4827bcc61b124ed","tid":746377,"uid":43173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"黑社會入會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要兄弟定要黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f236d08961df47d77c1956087ea176b5b7b36f4f","tid":746377,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"禽流感, sars, 伊波拉"},{"pid":"ef8b940ed7d8e5f5517210b2eaf5846129cc714d","tid":746377,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"佢哋會唔會袋定黃紙番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos